fi.paivola.mapserver.core

Class Model

  • java.lang.Object
    • fi.paivola.mapserver.core.Model
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConnectionModel, ExtensionModel, GlobalModel, PointModel

    public abstract class Model
extends Object
    The base class for all models. Has some basic functions that you will surely find useful.

    Juhani
